Installation

**************************
Requirements
**************************
Java6 or above
Apache Ant 	http://ant.apache.org/


**************************
Steps
**************************
     We call the root directory as PROJ_ROOT
1. Run ant in PROJ_ROOT
     > ant
2. Fangorn distribution is compiled and copied into PROJ_ROOT/dist folder
3. PROJ_ROOT/dist/fangorn is now your distribution root (DIST_ROOT) folder
4. All commands in the README file, unless otherwise specified, must be 
   executed from DIST_ROOT

